                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi> I served my master honesty till this transaction and what money or goods I took out, I brought a right account of.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. RICHARDSON</hi>. Yes, he did—I took him out of charity—he has a decent home, and has been a respectable man in business himself.</p>
